OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780074357
OL,3,CAston Villa star John McGinn features
OL,4,Cin 25ft mural on side of superfan's
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA 25-foot mural in honour of Aston
OL,8,FVilla captain John McGinn is being
OL,9,Fpainted in his hometown in Scotland.
OL,11,FStreet art dedicated to the Scotland
OL,12,Fstar is being painted on a building in
OL,13,FClydebank, West Dunbartonshire, on the
OL,14,Fside of a superfan's home.
OL,16,FIt will take 10 days to complete, with
OL,17,Fthe finish date expected next week.
OL,19,FA team of five painters has worked on
OL,20,Fthe project and more than 60 brushes
OL,21,Fand 100 litres of paint have been used.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
