OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780074357
OL,3,CAston Villa star John McGinn features
OL,4,Cin 25ft mural on side of superfan's
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FOrganised by Barr's Irn-Bru,
OL,8,Fhomeowners may nominate their exterior
OL,9,Fwalls for a free football makeover
OL,10,Fahead of the World Cup to demonstrate
OL,11,Ftheir dedication to Scotland's most
OL,12,Fbeloved footballers.
OL,14,FMcGinn is part of Scotland's squad for
OL,15,Fthe 2026 World Cup in North America
OL,16,Fthis June, having played 85 times for
OL,17,Fthe national side and scoring 20 goals.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
