PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780074357
OL,3,CAston Villa star John McGinn features
OL,4,Cin 25ft mural on side of superfan's
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FIt also comes after John McGinn
OL,8,Fcaptained Aston Villa to victory in
OL,9,Fthe Europa League final against
OL,10,FFreiburg on 20 May, ending Villa's 44-
OL,11,Fyear wait for a European trophy.
OL,13,FLesley Reynolds, 59, and Paul
OL,14,FPatterson, 63, offered their home for
OL,15,Fthe project.
OL,17,FMs Reynolds said: "John McGinn is a
OL,18,Fhero to many ` but no more so than
OL,19,Fhere in Clydebank.
OL,26,@yD@SOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
