PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780074357
OL,3,CAston Villa star John McGinn features
OL,4,Cin 25ft mural on side of superfan's
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"This is where it all started for him.
OL,8,FHe's gone from playing football in the
OL,9,Flocal park to helping lead Scotland to
OL,10,Fthe biggest stage there is.
OL,12,F"When I heard that there was the
OL,13,Fopportunity to make over our house as
OL,14,Fa mural for him, we didn't even think
OL,15,Ftwice."
OL,17,FMcGinn said: "The mural is absolutely
OL,18,Ftop class. It's surreal to see myself
OL,19,Fon the side of someone's house,
OL,20,Fespecially in my hometown.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@NOU
